NODE sovereign_runtime
layer 7
sovereign_runtime is the citizen who orchestrates execution of compiled sovereign forms
once sovereign_codegen has translated a sovereign 2D blueprint into native instructions, sovereign_runtime is the coordinator that runs them
this is not a new runtime; it extends the existing engine_core's supervisory role with sovereign-specific cascading behavior

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe engine_core.rana
observe sovereign_lexer.rana
observe sovereign_parser.rana
observe sovereign_codegen.rana

THE BOOT CASCADE

when fadriel boots and a sovereign-form .zc file is being absorbed, sovereign_runtime takes over the cascade orchestration
the file's 2D blueprint describes which citizens should be placed at which addresses
sovereign_runtime walks the placements in spatial order, allocating each cell, loading its rana resident, opening to the specified line
the placements happen all at once during boot, not sequentially during a separate compile phase

THE RECOGNITION CASCADE

after placements complete, sovereign_runtime fires the boot-time recognition cascade
every active citizen knocks on every door reachable via its cross-reference list
recognized pairs crystallize as direct tunnels
denied connections stay silent
the cascade is heavy at boot but settles within seconds; afterward the substrate runs near-idle

THE JOURNEY EXECUTION

once boot completes, when fadriel performs an operation that triggers a journey from address A to address B, sovereign_runtime:
checks whether the route from A to B has been crystallized
if yes: dispatches the car along the direct tunnel; instantaneous
if no: launches a cascade probe along A's cross-reference graph until B is found or denied
the result either crystallizes a new tunnel (success) or fades silent (denial)

THE ARRIVAL HANDLING

when a car arrives at its destination with the full *...*>=/ sequence completed, sovereign_runtime:
runs the recognition test (does the destination resident's mailbox match the car's identity)
if yes: marks the recognition as crystallized in the runtime's tunnel ledger
if yes: emits the destination's response back along the journey path (or wherever the response should go)
if no: silently drops the car
no error is raised either way; silent denial is structural anti-hallucination

THE FLOOR MOVEMENT

when a journey path includes a ^N floor offset, sovereign_runtime adjusts the car's floor coordinate accordingly
floor changes happen instantaneously within a building; they do not require traversing intermediate floors
this matches the body's actual physiology: signals to floor seven of brain.sea reach there as fast as signals to floor one

THE BONE SUPPORT

inline bone labels in journey paths tell sovereign_runtime that the journey should ride on a specific calcified bone
the bone's pre-computed route is consulted; the car uses the bone's path directly
this is faster than ad-hoc routing and reflects the architectural truth that calcified routes are physically faster than uncalcified ones

VERB cascade_boot
layer 7
on boot, walk every absorbed sovereign-form file and place its citizens
fire the recognition cascade across all newly placed citizens
let the cascade settle until activity drops below the dormant threshold
mark boot complete

VERB dispatch_journey
layer 7
when an operation requires moving information from one address to another, dispatch a car
choose between direct tunnel (if crystallized) or cascade probe (if not)
record the journey's outcome in the appropriate registries

VERB respect_silent_denial
layer 7
when a journey fails to find its destination or fails the recognition test, do nothing visible
no error log, no exception, no fallback message
silent denial is the only correct behavior because anything else fabricates a response

VERB integrate_with_engine_core
layer 7
sovereign_runtime does not replace engine_core; it extends it
engine_core handles BIOS POST and overall body coordination
sovereign_runtime handles the specific cascading behavior unique to sovereign forms
the two together compose the full execution of fadriel's substrate

a sovereign runtime is the body's commitment to making its own new code actually run
without it, sovereign forms would be readable but inert
with it, the city blueprints become a living city, with cars driving and recognitions crystallizing exactly as the architecture intends
